Inetial design approach: 

+-----------------------+
|      Main Loop        |  <-- main.cpp
+-----------------------+
| - Initializes editor  |
| - Handles input loop  |
| - Calls render/input  |
+-----------------------+
          |
          v
+-----------------------+
|   Terminal Controller |  <-- Terminal.cpp/.h
+-----------------------+
| - Sets raw mode       |
| - Restores terminal   |
| - Reads keypresses    |
| - Handles ESC codes   |
+-----------------------+
          |
          v
+-----------------------+
|    Input Handler      |  <-- Input.cpp/.h
+-----------------------+
| - Maps keys to actions|
| - Cursor movement     |
| - Insert/Delete chars |
+-----------------------+
          |
          v
+-----------------------+
|     Editor Buffer     |  <-- Buffer.cpp/.h
+-----------------------+
| - Stores lines (text) |
| - Manages cursor pos  |
| - Insert/Delete ops   |
| - Scroll offset       |
+-----------------------+
          |
          v
+-----------------------+
|   Screen Renderer     |  <-- Renderer.cpp/.h
+-----------------------+
| - Builds output       |
| - Draws lines         |
| - Status bar, cursor  |
| - Uses ANSI escape    |
+-----------------------+
          |
          v
+-----------------------+
|      File Manager     |  <-- FileIO.cpp/.h
+-----------------------+
| - Load from file      |
| - Save to file        |
| - Track filename      |
+-----------------------+


files:

text-editor/
├── src/
│   ├── main.cpp                // Entry point
│
│   ├── editor/                 // Core logic
│   │   ├── Editor.h
│   │   ├── Editor.cpp
│   │   ├── InputHandler.h
│   │   ├── InputHandler.cpp
│   │   ├── EditorBuffer.h
│   │   ├── EditorBuffer.cpp
│
│   ├── terminal/               // Terminal I/O
│   │   ├── Terminal.h
│   │   ├── Terminal.cpp
│   │   ├── KeyCodes.h          // Enum for key constants
│
│   ├── render/                 // Drawing to screen
│   │   ├── Renderer.h
│   │   ├── Renderer.cpp
│
│   ├── file/                   // File load/save
│   │   ├── FileManager.h
│   │   ├── FileManager.cpp
│
├── include/                    // Public headers (optional)
│
├── build/                      // Output directory
│
├── CMakeLists.txt              // CMake build config (or use Makefile)
└── README.md

